Package: exhibit
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, libetk, libepsilon
Suggests: enlightenment
Description: the Etk image viewer
 Exhibit is an image viewer that uses Etk as its toolkit.
 Exhibit supports  image previews for image types supported
 by Evas and allows for  directory changing using a point
 and click interface or a text input box with tab
 autocompletion support.
 Common operations include:
 - rotation / flipping
 - sharpen / blur
 - saving
 - resizing (needs implementation)
 - zooming in and out (needs implementation)
 - drag and drop (needs implementation)
 - image sorting (needs implementation).
